Contract award and date of first delivery delay due to DCMA withhold of authorization to proceed due to safety and quality CARS and 22 February 2014 explosive incident at ordnance sub-contractor.  Production resumed October 2014.  Contract award also delayed to comply with legal requirements for sole source procurement.  Will combine FY14/FY15 buy to achieve economies of scale and meet F-35A/F-35B IOC requirements.
